dct_title_s: A topographical map of the southwestern Highlands with the southwest portion of Kittatinny Valley
dct_description_sm: Geological Survey of New Jersey. Atlas Sheet 2 (Southwestern Highlands) (1885) New Jersey Geological Survey Relief shown by 20 feet contour interval and spot heights.
